caller_intent: Amani Duke from Reliance Insurance is following up on insurance proposals and quotes sent to Stephanie, seeking to confirm her receipt and arrange a callback.
resolution_steps: Maddie (agent) checks Stephanie's availability and informs Amani she is currently busy in the kitchen.
Amani agrees to leave a message for Stephanie.
Maddie confirms Stephanie will call back this afternoon as previously agreed.
Call concludes with mutual thanks and goodbye.
summary: Amani Duke from Reliance Insurance follows up on insurance proposals for Stephanie, who is unavailable. The agent takes a message and confirms Stephanie will call back this afternoon. The call concludes with a pending callback from Stephanie.
